<note n="0143002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0143002">Tadyatyā, same, samavati, śamitaśatru, aṅkure, manṅkure, mārajite, karāṭe, keyūre, oghavati, ohokayati, viśaṭhanirmale, malāpanaye, okhare, kharograse, grasane, hemukhī, parāṅmukhī, śamitāni sarvagrahabandhanāni, nigṛhītāḥ sar vaparapravādinaḥ, vimuktā mārapāśāḥ, sthāpitā buddhamudrāḥ samudghātitāḥ sarvamārāḥ, acalitapadapariśuddhyā vigacchanti sarvamārakarmāṇi.</note>
